{"tid":2000761,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［索尼粉］Playstation 惹眾怒　PSN 5月會員限時免費令人失望致大量投訴","createTime":"2020-05-04T05:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T15:41:07.000Z","uid":14075,"like":144,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"64e8373735f7d8e2dbe74f62a8873758d3e07ece","tid":2000761,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"在四月末Sony Playstation官方公佈了各服的五月PS+會免陣容，港服和歐美服一致為《Cities：Skylines》以及《Farming Simulator 19》兩款「種田」遊戲。這樣的陣容引起了大批玩家的不滿，<a href=\"http://甚至有激動的PS玩家跑去change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%94%9A%E8%87%B3%E6%9C%89%E6%BF%80%E5%8B%95%E7%9A%84PS%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E8%B7%91%E5%8E%BBchange.org&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWXw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=7e180404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">甚至有激動的PS玩家跑去change.org</a>發起聯名請願要求官方更換遊戲，截至發帖請願已經有13,437人參與。<br />\n<br />\n此次會免引起如此大的風波恐怕還是因為前一周的疑似會免陣容洩露消息，ResetEra論壇上在4月27日有人爆料稱五月會免將會是《Dying Light》和《Dark Soulｓ：Remastered》，兩款重磅作品令不少沒有入手的玩家心生期待，結果拿到手的卻是令動作遊戲愛好者感到味同嚼蠟的《Farming Simulator》，因此玩家群體中才爆發瞭如此大規模的抗議活動。<br />\n<br />\n如今PS歐服的官方會免披露影片Dislike數已經達到了1500:10000，請願發起人稱這樣的陣容讓玩家感到哭笑不得，彷彿像個愚人節笑話。該請願直接針對PlayStation總裁Jim Ryan，要求其做出改變更換五月會免陣容，並稱這麼做才能夠幫助所有孤獨隔離在家的玩家，而不是在最需要&ldquo;好遊戲&rdquo;的時候種玉米（指Farming Simulator）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gameapps.hk/news/38933/playstation-plus-free-game\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F38933%2Fplaystation-plus-free-game&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWXw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=ecacc7b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gameapps.hk/news/38933/playstation-plus-free-game</a><br />\n<br />\n索尼狗咁既質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f0802dec18dba968f044a4924b83982b761985","tid":2000761,"uid":285514,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:35:30.000Z","m